==發行==
電影於2016年1月22日在[[日舞影展|日舞影展]]上首映<ref name="thr-sam">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/swiss-army-man-sundance-review-858537 |title='Swiss Army Man': Sundance Review |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=January 22, 2016 |accessdate=2016-01-24 |archive-date=2016-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160124023148/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/swiss-army-man-sundance-review-858537 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年1月30日，該片被[[A24_(公司)|A24]]收購獲得在美國的發行權<ref name="Brent Lang">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/a24-daniel-radcliffe-swiss-army-man-sundance-1201692377/ |title=A24 Lands Daniel Radcliffe Corpse Movie ‘Swiss Army Man’ (EXCLUSIVE) |work=Variety |date=January 29, 2016 |accessdate=2016-01-29 |archive-date=2016-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131080813/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/a24-daniel-radcliffe-swiss-army-man-sundance-1201692377/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。原定於2016年6月17日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web |author=Maane Khatchatourian |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/daniel-radcliffe-farting-corpse-swiss-army-man-trailer-1201744802/ |title=‘Swiss Army Man’ Trailer: Daniel Radcliffe Is a Farting Corpse |publisher=Variety |date=2016-04-04 |accessdate=2016-04-08 |archive-date=2016-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408015008/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/daniel-radcliffe-farting-corpse-swiss-army-man-trailer-1201744802/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但一個星期後改至6月24日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=swissarmyman.htm|title=Swiss Army Man|website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=April 22, 2016|archive-date=2016-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160607065322/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=swissarmyman.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。A24還收購了全球的發行權，並獲得了國外的合作電影發行商<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/swiss-army-man-worldwide-distribution-a24-sundance-daniel-radcliffe-1201732184/|title=A24 To Handle ‘Swiss Army Man’ Global Release In Company